      "value": "<p>To follow this Stylized Looks overview for RenderMan for Houdini, make sure to use the great demo scene created by Ernst Janssen Groesbeek of <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.9to3animation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">9 to 3 Animation</a>:</p><p>Download the scene in the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH/pages/20906310\" rel=\"nofollow\">example scenes</a>.</p><p /><iframe align=\"middle\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"846ca213-0959-4667-935a-714453c3f629\" data-macro-id=\"e6b44b469aaad2190bf81128ada135d72e9b3bb54eda2169429559730e35c1c3\" data-macro-name=\"iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"600\" marginwidth=\"960\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-orientation-lock allow-pointer-lock allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"yes\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/524321771\" width=\"960\">\n    \n</iframe>\n<p /><p>Ship concept by Ian McQue.</p><p>Robot concept by Ruslan Safarov.</p><p>Models by Cheyenne Chapel, Aliya Chen, Damian Kwiatkowski, Alyssa Minko, Anthony Muscarella, and Miguel Zozaya</p><p>© Disney/Pixar - RenderMan &quot;Shipshape&quot; Art Challenge</p>"
